    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "just to clarify, you are requesting a `%pyplot [backend]` magic that does\n\n```\n%matplotlib [backend]\nfrom matplotlib import pyplot as plt\n```\n\n?\n\nIf so, put this in your profile's startup folder:\n\n``` python\ndef pyplot(line=''):\n    get_ipython().magic(u'%matplotlib '+ line)\n    get_ipython().run_cell('import matplotlib.pyplot as plt')\n\n\nget_ipython().magics_manager.register_function(pyplot)\ndel(pyplot)\n```\n"
  },
